1) Ensure you have Java 1.8 and Maven on you local system.
2) If you want to run the test on ChromeDriver, please download chrome driver from Seleniumhq.org
   and provide the path to chromedriver on "ColorPageTest" class.
3) Open up the project using an IDE, I used Intellij IDEA
4) Navigate to the test folder
5) Context click on the "ColorPageTest" class and hit run
6) OR using the command line navigate to the project structure and type "mvn verify"